romance.title: Romance
romance.description: Unrequited longing, larger-than-life passion, and guilty pleasures — watch these titles in the name of love.

11219.title: 200 Pound Beauty
11219.description: A large woman who sings for a famous Korean pop star undergoes a drastic makeover and physical transformation, aided by extensive plastic surgery.

65270.title: Come Undone
65270.description: Despite having a good career and a loving boyfriend, a young woman risks it all when she begins a steamy, tumultuous affair with a married man.

289851.title: Spread
289851.description: High-end lothario Nikki sleeps his way into a life of privilege all while crashing at the Hollywood Hills home of a middle-aged female attorney.

299580.title: The Big Easy
299580.description: A new female district attorney is unhappy with the gangs and corruption in New Orleans and bonds with a detective in this sultry crime thriller.

299633.title: The Maid
299633.description: A troubled teenager visits his estranged father and begins a passionate, life-changing affair with the older woman who works at the house.

300454.title: Moonstruck
300454.description: Loretta Castorini (Cher), a bookkeeper from Brooklyn, New York, finds herself in a difficult situation when she falls for the brother of the man she has agreed to marry.

300457.title: Much Ado About Nothing
300457.description: Shakespeare's classic comedy tells the story of two couples: confirmed bachelor Benedick and caustic Beatrice, and young Claudio and innocent Hero. Playful bickering defines one couple, whereas romance and betrayal describe the other.

300464.title: Return To Me
300464.description: In this romantic comedy, tragedy unites Bob and Grace, who have instant chemistry. But there’s more to their relationship than chance.

301924.title: Man of the West
301924.description: A reformed outlaw is left abandoned in a remote area after he intervenes in a train robbery, where he unexpectedly runs into his old gang.

302153.title: The Cutting Edge
302153.description: After suffering a career-ending head injury, a talented hockey player trains with a difficult figure skater to compete in the 1992 Winter Olympics.

302254.title: Solomon and Sheba
302254.description: In this biblical epic, the king of Israel proclaims which son will succeed him but a neglected brother and distant rulers threaten the new king.

302263.title: Untamed Heart
302263.description: A waitress and a busboy start a whirlwind romance after he rescues her after work from an attack in this tale of two souls destined to be together.

302320.title: The Cutting Edge: Going For The Gold
302320.description: In her road to recovery from a career-threatening injury, a young Olympic-bound figure skater finds an unlikely partner in an cocky skater boy.

304797.title: Benny & Joon
304797.description: A quirky, romantic drama about two misfits who come together as a result of an unusual poker game.

304809.title: Support Your Local Gunfighter
304809.description: When a charming con man is mistaken for an infamous gunfighter, he decides to impersonate the gunfighter so he can earn money to pay his debts.

305010.title: Body of Evidence
305010.description: This erotic thriller follows the trial of a woman who is accused of murdering a wealthy old man with her dangerous sexual proclivities.

306936.title: The Man In The Moon
306936.description: Set in the South during the 1950s, a fourteen-year-old girl comes to terms with one of life's most powerful yet fleeting feelings: adolescent love.

312180.title: The Hot Spot
312180.description: After robbing a Texas bank, a used car salesman finds himself at the romantic mercies of two very different women who both want his love.

312182.title: Jason's Lyric
312182.description: In inner-city Houston, a man from a struggling family finds love and hope with a woman named Lyric. But secrets from the past threaten his future.

312409.title: The Apartment
312409.description: A corporate drone hatches a scheme for success: Let the execs use his apartment for “dates.” It goes beautifully, until his love interest gets hurt.

312421.title: Marty
312421.description: Ernest Borgnine stars as Marty, a lonely Bronx butcher who gives up on love -- until he meets an equally lonely school teacher in this charming story.

314149.title: Puppylove
314149.description: When a free-spirited girl befriends a young teenager, they leave childhood behind to embrace a dangerous world of clubbing and sex with strange men.

315180.title: Erosion
315180.description: An unhappy housewife is thrilled by her affair with a mysterious man when they break into strangers’ homes and role play to escape their lives.

316454.title: Secretary
316454.description: Hoping to recover from her troubled past, a socially awkward woman becomes a secretary for an eccentric lawyer who is aroused by her obedience.

339389.title: The Ultimate Gift
339389.description: The death of his grandfather catapults trust-fund baby Jason on an improbable journey of self-discovery, making him rethink what he truly values.

369729.title: The Thomas Crown Affair
369729.description: A millionaire playboy steals a priceless work of art and strikes up a fiery romance with the brilliant insurance investigator who works to take him down.

382212.title: Accidentally Engaged
382212.description: An aspiring actress pretends to be engaged to a famous actor to impress her friends. When the actor finds out, he agrees to continue the lie.

387155.title: Love Everlasting
387155.description: A high school senior escapes his abusive stepfather and sparks fly when he meets a fellow outcast in a small, middle-of-nowhere town.

389499.title: Picture This
389499.description: Mandy lands a date to the party of the year with her dream guy, Drew. But, she'll have to battle her overprotective dad and Drew's ex-girlfriend.

389502.title: The Cutting Edge 3: Chasing the Dream
389502.description: When his partner injures herself, a figure skater finds a last-minute replacement for a competition: a beautiful and talented hockey player.

389515.title: Griffin and Phoenix
389515.description: A poignant romantic comedy about two people who face a seemingly insurmountable obstacle that may stand between them and a last chance at love.

389846.title: The Other End of the Line
389846.description: When a woman working at a call center in India falls for a man over the phone, she travels to San Francisco to see if it is true love after all.

393552.title: My Man Godfrey
393552.description: A scatterbrained socialite hires vagrant Godfrey as a butler for her eccentric family. But there's more to Godfrey than meets the eye.

394072.title: Original Sin
394072.description: In this erotic thriller, a beautiful, mail-order bride plays a long con on her new, wealthy husband but love and passion were not part of the plan.

417716.title: Buffalo 66
417716.description: Billy Brown just got out of jail. Now he’s going to serve some real time. He’s going home.

448663.title: Leaving Las Vegas
448663.description: Determined to end it all, a committed drinker picks Vegas as his last stop, but he finds comfort with a kind prostitute who needs help of her own.

448828.title: Caveman
448828.description: Set in prehistoric times, a thoughtful-but-goofy cave dweller tries to woo a gorgeous woman in his tribe away from her much stronger and dumber mate.

451914.title: Two Night Stand
451914.description: A snowstorm forces two people who made an online connection to unwillingly extend their one-night stand as the blizzard goes through the night.

455985.title: Sex, Guaranteed
455985.description: When a heartbroken roofer swears off sex, a hard-partying financier introduces him to a beautiful escort to get him to reconsider his decision.

458075.title: Autumn in New York
458075.description: When a middle-aged playboy and successful restauranteur meets his match in a woman half his age, a rare, precious, and fragile romance blooms.

463228.title: Black Coffee
463228.description: A man finds romance after he’s fired from his family business but the new couple’s happiness is threatened when both of their exes return.

466252.title: Getting Played
466252.description: Three friends compete to prove what they think they know about men by seducing the same stranger, but the man they choose doesn’t play by their rules.

466618.title: Teen Witch
466618.description: On the cusp of her 16th birthday, a high-school nobody discovers she has magical powers that may help her cast a spell on her dream guy.

468974.title: Sweet Home Carolina
468974.description: A burnt-out Los Angeles ad executive inherits a huge house in rural South Carolina, but she has to live there for a year before it’s hers to own.

475177.title: All Things Fair
475177.description: A forbidden relationship between a teen student and his adult, female teacher in World War II-era Sweden has consequences neither of them expect.

486540.title: Switch
486540.description: When your wife's not happy with the sex at home, sometimes she has to make a switch.

496441.title: Regresa
496441.description: Tras someterse a una terapia para resolver su problemas matrimoniales, María despierta de una hipnosis creyendo ser una princesa vasca del siglo XV.

504505.title: Before the Dawn
504505.description: Lila is a lonely high school teacher who just wants a fresh start, and finds it with Jason, her troubled student who falls for her.

506263.title: Candy
506263.description: When a poet and an art student form a codependent relationship with each other and heroin, they face a series of troubling choices.

507677.title: Absolution
507677.description: A girl born with the power to absorb the pain and fear of others has to maximize it to save the man she loves while being guided by those she’s saved.

507852.title: Above the Shadows
507852.description: A woman who became literally invisible to others after her mother died works as a sleuth until meeting a jaded fighter, the only one who can see her.

508260.title: Longing Nights
508260.description: Four twenty-somethings, two men and two women, navigate the nightlife of Madrid, Spain as a way to bridge the erotic loneliness in their lives.

510715.title: Trois 2: Pandora's Box
510715.description: A prominent psychologist in a passionless marriage is seduced by a new client to join an underground sex club where her life takes a dangerous turn.

521796.title: Utopians
521796.description: A student finds himself attracted to his outspoken male professor and undergoes an experience that transforms his life forever.

528422.title: Not Cinderella's Type
528422.description: A modern-day girl, living with her aunt, uncle, and bothersome cousins, learns to see with the heart, as she chooses between two very different boys.

534015.title: The Choice
534015.description: A carefree bachelor and a medical student in her own committed relationship must make a choice of the heart in this heart-lifting romance drama.

535453.title: The Guest House
535453.description: Recently dumped by her high school sweetheart, a goth girl starts an affair with her father’s new employee who moves into their L.A. guest house.

540237.title: The Lover
540237.description: The forbidden and risky romance between a French teenager and a wealthy, older Chinese man in 1929 French Indochina has the power to ruin their lives.

544023.title: The Brothers
544023.description: Engaging romantic comedy about 4 young Black men whose success in life is incomplete, a fact they face when their resident playboy gets engaged.

548642.title: Kiss Me
548642.description: Two women in their 30s feel an instant attraction upon meeting at their parents’ engagement party, realizing they will be stepsisters, and maybe more.

557272.title: Letters From the Heart
557272.description: When Hope travels to a small town for her grandmother’s funeral, she learns that she’s inherited two million dollars, under one condition.

561890.title: Plug Love
561890.description: After a woman ends her unfaithful relationship, she discovers the value of true love in a world that often prioritizes material wealth.

569450.title: Held Up
569450.description: After a man is dumped by his fiancée in a desert town, he is taken hostage by robbers while he tries to make amends with his love.

574217.title: Obsesión (Doblado)
574217.description: Simon hereda una casa de campo en Francia a la que viaja con su esposo y sus dos hijos. Su sueño es renovarla, pero a medida que avanza la reconstrucción, cae en un romance prohibido

589088.title: Practical Magic
589088.description: Two magical New England sisters must outwit and overcome their family curse, which dooms the men they love to die in tragic circumstances.

591107.title: The House Bunny
591107.description: A former Playboy model finds a new path in life when she becomes an unlikely mentor and role model to a sorority full of studious young college students.

599994.title: Two Weeks Notice
599994.description: For five years Lucy has been treated more like a nanny than a Harvard-trained lawyer, chosen George's clothes, arranged his divorce, lost sleep and gained an ulcer, but now she's calling it quits. She gives George her Two Weeks Notice.  George finally agrees to let her go ... if she finds her own replacement. After a challenging search, Lucy hires an ambitious young lawyer with an obvious eye for her new boss. Now, as she joins her devoted boyfriend for an adventure at sea, Lucy is finally free of George. Or is she? With Lucy sailing out of his life, George must decide if it's ever too late to say "I love you."

599997.title: Wedding Crashers
599997.description: Owen Wilson (Starsky & Hutch) and Vince Vaughn (Old School) star as John Beckwith and Jeremy Klein, two partying divorce attorneys--and committed womanizers--who have figured out a surefire way to meet women: they crash weddings. But the guys' happy-go-lucky lives change abruptly when John unexpectedly falls in love with a bridesmaid (Rachel McAdams - The Notebook). Things become even more complicated when the men discover that the object of John's affection is the daughter of the United States Secretary of the Treasury (Christopher Walken - Catch Me If You Can) in the engaging romantic comedy Wedding Crashers.

605387.title: Leap Year
605387.description: Una oaxaqueña avecindada en la Ciudad de México mata su soledad con varios amantes fugaces hasta entregarse a una peligrosa relación sadomasoquista.

605625.title: The Slut
605625.description: A vibrant, beautiful mother enjoys meaningless sexual trysts, until a young veterinarian falls under her spell and challenges her polyamorous ways.

608936.title: For the Love of Ruth
608936.description: A warm-hearted Christmas film  about an accomplished woman’s return home from Atlanta where she starts to reconnect with a noble former classmate.

614728.title: 4th Man Out
614728.description: A laid-back car mechanic has the challenge of his life when he decides to finally let his blue-collar best friends know that he is gay.

615088.title: It Had to Be You
615088.description: Two strangers fall for each other over the course of a few eventful days. The only problem? They’re both about to get married to other people!

615952.title: A Marriage of Convenience
615952.description: A successful businesswoman gives up her career to raise her late sister's son and soon falls for the boy's father.

617447.title: Pretty Woman
617447.description: Julia Roberts stars as a witty prostitute who charms a serious businessman, as the two unlikely lovers fall for each other over the course of a week.

620779.title: Siberia
620779.description: After an American diamond merchant and his lover fall into a bad business deal in Russia, they must evade crossfire between the buyer and Feds.

622678.title: Water for Elephants
622678.description: During the Great Depression, a veterinary student, recently orphaned and suddenly adrift, joins the circus and falls for the animal trainer’s wife.

622846.title: Australia
622846.description: With the threat of war looming, a landowner in Australia fights to keep her cattle and her land with the help of a seasoned ranch hand.

623023.title: Demonios Tus Ojos
623023.description: Por andar viendo una web erótica, Oliver se topa con un video explícito protagonizado por su hermana menor y perturbado viaja a buscarla.

625138.title: My One and Only
625138.description: This unusual road trip movie follows a mother driving her two sons from New York to Hollywood, on her quest to find a man to take care of them all.

625513.title: Jab We Met
625513.description: A suicidal industrial worker sees his life completely change when he meets a free-spirited and talkative young woman on the train who bonds with him.

629964.title: El Amor Es Imperfecto (Doblado)
629964.description: Una hermosa perfeccionista obsesiva de 35 años se ve atraida por una joven de 18 que le ofrece pasión y un hombre mayor que le ofrece estabilidad.

637438.title: Infidelity
637438.description: Struggling within a passionless marriage, a woman decides to fulfill her own desires, by breaking away from her husband and the woman she once was.

637827.title: Don Jon
637827.description: A Jersey guy addicted to porn meets a charming and beautiful woman whom he hopes to pursue a real relationship with, but his habits get in the way.

638893.title: Deliver Us From Eva
638893.description: The formidable Eva Dandridge is considered an angel by her sisters, but their men think she’s a devil. Can a new suave player win her heart?

639274.title: La Ley Del Monte
639274.description: Una pareja de niños juran amarse toda la vida y graban sus nombres en la penca de un maguey, pero los padres de ella están en contra de su relación.

641418.title: Los Hijos De María Morales
641418.description: Estos hermanos son un par de alegres parranderos, cantadores, jugadores y mujeriegos, y la única que puede aplacar sus travesuras es su severa madre.

641484.title: Brown Sugar
641484.description: A record label producer and his longtime best friend come to the discovery that they’re in love almost immediately after one of them gets engaged.

641581.title: Somewhere in Time
641581.description: A playwright visiting a hotel falls in love with an actress pictured in a 1912 photo and uses self-hypnosis to go 68 years back in time to meet her.

650036.title: Dirty Work
650036.description: A young fashion graduate becomes a personal assistant for an over-the-top erotic novelist, starting an affair that gets her drawn into a murder plot.

654016.title: Something New
654016.description: A workaholic accountant living in Los Angeles must decide between a predictable IBM (Ideal Black Man) and her free-spirited white landscaper.

655527.title: Cam Girls
655527.description: Three young women, bored and frustrated by the lack of human contact during the pandemic lockdown, turn to their webcams to save their love lives.

660771.title: Call Me: The Rise and Fall of Heidi Fleiss
660771.description: The true story of “The Hollywood Madam,” who catered to wealthy Hollywood types, corporate execs, and Arab sheiks, until the law caught up with her.

661142.title: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse
661142.description: The third film in the Twilight franchise. Torn between Edward and Jacob, Bella must also confront a vengeful vampire and a string of grisly murders.

661144.title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn: Part 1
661144.description: The fourth film in the Twilight franchise. A marriage, honeymoon and child bring unforeseen and shocking developments for Bella and Edward.

664749.title: 10 Things I Hate About You
664749.description: On the first day at his new school, Cameron instantly falls for Bianca, the gorgeous girl of his dreams. The only problem? She isn't allowed to date.

666107.title: Status Update
666107.description: After his parents split up, a struggling teenager stumbles upon a life-altering, magical app that causes his social media updates to come true.

668282.title: The Wedding Date
668282.description: A story about the road to finding true love. Kat’s single-girl anxiety prompts her to hire a male escort to pose as her date at her sister’s wedding.

670534.title: Trois
670534.description: Bored in his daily routine, a man convinces his wife to bring a third party into the bedroom. Trouble erupts when the other woman refuses to let go.

672301.title: The 40-Year-Old Virgin
672301.description: Nice guy Andy has lived his whole life without "doing it." Now, his misguided pals are helping him reverse his fortunes—and maybe even find true love.

675509.title: Farmer Seeking Love
675509.description: A successful reality-tv show producer convinces a small-town farmer to be the next bachelor on her hit dating program' Head Over Heels.'

675531.title: Decadencia
675531.description: Anabel, una hermosa joven colombiana, trabaja como anfitriona, conoce a Oscar, se enamora y comienza a caer en los juegos sexuales de su pareja.

675534.title: El Peluquero
675534.description: El peluquero se enfrenta a los poderes mágicos de la bruja Tomasa y junto a sus amigos parte en busca del verdadero amor y fortuna.

675797.title: Destination Love
675797.description: On a remote island in New Zealand, a young woman and local vineyard owner hope to create the perfect destination wedding for her best friends.

676687.title: Sleeping With Other People
676687.description: Lainey and Jake, neither of whom have a great track record with monogamy, form a platonic friendship that soon develops into something more.

678422.title: Ninety Sunsets
678422.description: After tragedy leaves her 10-year-old son unable to speak, a mom gains a new perspective on destiny when a mishap becomes a love she never saw coming.

683309.title: The Love Witch
683309.description: A modern-day witch in California uses spells and magic to get men to fall in love with her in this tribute to 1960’s Technicolor thrillers.

684099.title: Plus One
684099.description: Long-time friends Alice and Ben make an agreement to be one another's plus-ones as they power through an endless parade of insufferable weddings.

686449.title: Honey
686449.description: Pulse-pounding music and awesome dance moves ignite this exhilarating story of one dancer’s passion, courage and determination to follow her dreams.

686493.title: Intimate Betrayals
686493.description: Love, lies and deceit are common things in relationships. What happens when this trio comes knocking on Danielle's door? Who's there to cover her?

690246.title: Swingers (Sub Esp)
690246.description: A pesar de la naturaleza insegura de Diana, ella y su marido Julián están de acuerdo con la idea de experimentar sexualmente con otra pareja.

690311.title: The Reader
690311.description: In post-WWII Germany, a law student finds the older woman with whom he had an affair eight years ago, among Nazi prison guards being tried for murder.

693653.title: The Exchange
693653.description: Sabina and Esther's relationship is pushed to its breaking point when Annie, an international exchange student from Mexico, comes to stay.

693660.title: Infamous
693660.description: Two young lovers rob their way across the southland, posting their numerous exploits on social media and gaining fame and followers.

695341.title: Tyler Perry's Why Did I Get Married Too?
695341.description: Four couples on an annual retreat struggle to save their marriages while each of them battles their own financial, physical and emotional issues.

696806.title: A Walk to Remember
696806.description: North Carolina teens Landon Carter and Jamie Sullivan are thrown together after one gets into trouble and is sentenced to community service.

697861.title: Will to Love
697861.description: The CEO of a multi-million dollar corporation will have to find a bride if he plans on inheriting his grandfather's company and estate.

699030.title: Another Gay Movie (Director's Cut)
699030.description: Out of the closet and crazy horny, a naive high schooler and his loud-and-proud besties take a raunchy ride on the road to losing their virginity.

699046.title: Love Actually…Sucks!
699046.description: An interconnected group of people in Hong Kong experience the dark side of love in this ensemble drama inspired by real life crimes of the heart.

699110.title: Sex, Lies, and Sugar
699110.description: More than recipes get swapped in 1960’s suburbia when modern American housewives host dinner parties that soon become boozy, flirtatious and wild.

700643.title: Boxed In
700643.description: Up-and-coming boxer Ria is focused only on her sport—until she meets Tuga, and learns that a life without love really isn't a life at all.

701466.title: Beauty and the Billionaire
701466.description: To help out her brother, Addison is forced to travel with his picky billionaire boss when they start to see more in each other than they thought.

701801.title: A Werewolf Boy (Subbed)
701801.description: Summoned by an unexpected phone call, a woman visits the cottage she used to live in as a child and recalls the memory of a boy she knew 47 years ago.

702432.title: Girl/Girl Scene 1984
702432.description: Gorgeous Bridget, her girlfriend Evan, sassy Trista, sweetheart Dov and party girl Ryan live and love as young lesbians in a not-so-modern world.

702538.title: Por Tu Maldito Amor
702538.description: Al regresar a su pueblo, un ganadero pelea con el actual esposo de su antiguo amor y una machorra y el dueño de una plantación lo ayudan.

702670.title: Bellas De Noche
702670.description: Un boxeador retirado entra a trabajar en un centro nocturno donde se enamora de una de las bailarinas y tiene que lidiar con varios personajes.

704897.title: Through a Boy's Eyes
704897.description: A collection of award-winning short films about the journeys of boys turning into young men, as their perceptions of those around them evolve.

706418.title: Cougar Hunting
706418.description: Three randy 20-somethings head to Aspen, hoping to meet rich, older women. Their adventures take a series of hilarious and unexpected turns.

706471.title: The Sleepover
706471.description: Ex-girlfriends Tabby and Heidi spend the night together at a friend’s sleepover. Can they move past old feelings, or will they fall in love again?

710352.title: Whatcha Wearin'?
710352.description: To repair her relationship, Yun-jung makes a phone sex call to her boyfriend only to learn the heartsick man she misdialed would become her true love.

710949.title: Who Made the Potatoe Salad?
710949.description: A young San Diego police officers travels to Los Angeles with his fiancée to meet her dysfunctional family and announce their engagement.

712009.title: Curiosa
712009.description: Explores a fiery love triangle in 1895 Paris between a dandy and poet on the verge of fame, his friend and the cheeky daughter of their mentor.

712888.title: Just Married
712888.description: When two young newlyweds set off to Europe, family tensions and lots of bad luck turn their dream trip into a honeymoon from hell.

712892.title: Hope Floats
712892.description: After learning about her husband's affair, a former beauty queen moves back to her tiny Texas hometown and reunites with an old flame.

713166.title: Frankie Meets Jack
713166.description: Sparks fly when Frankie meets Jack, the veterinarian who rescues her dog from near death. They seem destined to be together, but there's one problem: Jack is already engaged.

714943.title: Don Juan DeMarco
714943.description: After losing his one true love and attempting suicide, a man who believes he’s the mythical Don Juan is placed in the care of a world-weary therapist.

715217.title: Vision Quest
715217.description: A gentle but driven 18-year-old underdog toils against the odds to become Washington state’s top wrestler while winning the heart of a young drifter.

715457.title: Swingers (Peliculas en Espanol)
715457.description: A pesar de su carácter inseguro, Diana y su marido aceptan la idea de experimentar sexualmente con otra pareja y ponen un anuncio en Internet.

716250.title: The Lover
716250.description: The mundane existence of a Tel-Aviv housewife is shaken up after a sensuous stranger enters her family’s home at the onset of the Yom Kippur War.

716298.title: Waves
716298.description: Traces the epic emotional journey of a suburban African-American family as they navigate love, forgiveness and coming together after a tragic loss.

717293.title: Simple Passion
717293.description: In this tale of lust and vulnerability, a mother falls into an addictive relationship with a Russian diplomat with whom she has nothing in common.

720943.title: Burlesque
720943.description: A small-town singer moves to the city for a chance at fame when she finds a glamorous nightclub packed with dancers and an owner in need of a star.

720953.title: St. Elmo's Fire
720953.description: Fresh out of college, a sax player, a party girl, a writer, and their other aimless friends search for their places in the real world.

723250.title: Bend It Like Beckham
723250.description: Despite the wishes of their traditional families, two young women from different walks of life aim for a career in professional soccer.

724347.title: The Best Man
724347.description: A Chicago author forces his old friend group to confront secrets from the past when he arrives in town for his best friend’s wedding with a new book.

724581.title: The Rewrite
724581.description: An Oscar-winning screenwriter is now left with nothing but a string of unsuccessful films, forcing him to take the job he hates most: teaching.

725788.title: Hampstead
725788.description: This sparklingly witty, London-set romance is based on the inspiring true story of a man's against-all-odds fight to save his home.

100000012.title: The Decoy Bride
100000012.description: A Hollywood starlet's plans for a remote island wedding get complicated when the decoy bride she hires to distract the paparazzi falls for the groom.

100000081.title: And Then There Was You
100000081.description: A newly divorced woman who’s soured on relationships meets a new man who challenges the boundaries of her trust and her ability to fall in love again.

100000203.title: Four of Hearts
100000203.description: In a desperate attempt to rekindle the passion in their marriage, a couple shares a steamy but ill-fated night with a pair of free-spirited friends.

100000206.title: I Do...I Did
100000206.description: A hilarious battle of wills ensues when a strange twist of fate leaves one bewildered man married to two beautiful, hot-blooded women.

100000282.title: 35 & Ticking
100000282.description: Centers around the lives of a group of friends who are approaching the age of 35 and are struggling to build the families they've always dreamed of.

100000293.title: Plus One at an Amish Wedding
100000293.description: Doctor April's new romance with handsome veterinarian Jesse seems perfect—until they get invited to a wedding with the Amish family he left behind.

100000326.title: Sunrise in Heaven
100000326.description: After a devastating car crash leaves her husband on life support, a woman must find strength in her faith as she faces the prospect of his passing.
